Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,处理得真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢
